
<style>
	.box{
		padding: 10px 0 0 0;
	}
</style>

<table>

<tr><td>
	<%if(@depositor.full_name == nil)%>
		Dear author [<%= @depositor.uni %>],
	<% else %>
		Dear <%= @depositor.full_name %>,
	<% end %>
</td></tr>
<tr><td class="box">
	A record with metadata about your recent deposit(s) to Academic Commons is now live on academiccommons.columbia.edu.  
</td></tr>	

<tr><td style="padding: 10px 0 5px 0;">As per your instructions, the files themselves are not available on Academic Commons at this time. They will become available on the dates listed below.</td></tr>

	<% @depositor.items_list.each do | item | %>
	   <tr><td style="padding: 5px 0 0 0;"><%= item.title %></td></tr>
	   <tr><td style="padding: 0 0 5px 0;"><a href="<%= item.handle %>"><%= item.handle %></a> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td style="padding: 0 0 5px 0;">Release date: <%= item.free_to_read_start_date %></td></tr>
	<% end %>

<tr><td class="box">
Thank you for contributing to Academic Commons. If you have any questions about your deposit, you can reach us by replying to this email.
</td></tr>
<tr><td class="box">
	
Sincerely,<br>
The Academic Commons Team,<br>
<a href="http://cdrs.columbia.edu">Center for Digital Research and Scholarship</a><br>
Columbia University Libraries / Information Services 	
	
</td></tr>

</table>




